{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-works-work-js","path":"/ifast/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"681f9f45-3b63-5018-aed6-b852677aab0d","excerpt":"Project Description iFast Express is a logistics service based in Dubai, moving deliveries across the UAE. The whole operation runs on Odoo…","html":"<h2>Project Description</h2>\n<p><strong>iFast Express</strong> is a logistics service based in Dubai, moving deliveries across the UAE. The whole operation runs on <strong>Odoo</strong>: every delivery moves through a live pipeline — awaiting pickup, collected, in sorting facility, out for delivery, delivered — with returns, cancellations, and lost/damaged handling tracked in the same flow. Around that core sit finance reports, fulfilment inventory, international pricing, and customer care, with multi-company support and a bilingual English/Arabic interface.</p>\n<p>The public site at ifast.express fronts the platform — company profile, shipment tracking, and the download door to the customer apps.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4da15d0b96e016762d7872aec222ee77/84d4d/image2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"The delivery operations dashboard\"\n        title=\"The delivery operations dashboard\"\n        src=\"/static/4da15d0b96e016762d7872aec222ee77/fcda8/image2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4da15d0b96e016762d7872aec222ee77/12f09/image2.png 148w,\n/static/4da15d0b96e016762d7872aec222ee77/e4a3f/image2.png 295w,\n/static/4da15d0b96e016762d7872aec222ee77/fcda8/image2.png 590w,\n/static/4da15d0b96e016762d7872aec222ee77/efc66/image2.png 885w,\n/static/4da15d0b96e016762d7872aec222ee77/c83ae/image2.png 1180w,\n/static/4da15d0b96e016762d7872aec222ee77/84d4d/image2.png 2996w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>What I did</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Built the delivery operations platform on Odoo — the delivery lifecycle pipeline, finance reports, fulfilment inventory, and international pricing</li>\n<li>Developed the dynamic frontend views with OWL JS</li>\n<li>Developed the public website with shipment tracking</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"iFast Express","category":"Odoo & Web Development","tags":["Odoo","OWL JS"],"description":"An Odoo-powered logistics platform for a Dubai delivery company — the full delivery lifecycle, finance, and fulfilment run from one system.","projectLink":"https://ifast.express/ifastexpress","date":"2025.06.20","image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":2,"src":"/static/600d98cc36242acfb6bf3138a9d1f987/73f08/image1.png","srcSet":"/static/600d98cc36242acfb6bf3138a9d1f987/57fc3/image1.png 300w,\n/static/600d98cc36242acfb6bf3138a9d1f987/f8eb5/image1.png 600w,\n/static/600d98cc36242acfb6bf3138a9d1f987/73f08/image1.png 1200w,\n/static/600d98cc36242acfb6bf3138a9d1f987/2af26/image1.png 1800w,\n/static/600d98cc36242acfb6bf3138a9d1f987/fc001/image1.png 2400w,\n/static/600d98cc36242acfb6bf3138a9d1f987/17531/image1.png 2996w","sizes":"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/ifast/","fileNo":11}},"staticQueryHashes":["63159454"]}